ResidueId — interface { chainId, seqId }
ChainData — interface { id, entityId, residues[] }
ElementData — interface { chainId, entityId, entityType, moleculeName, compIds[], residueCount, atomCount }
getFirstStructure(plugin) — retrieves loaded Structure from plugin hierarchy
selectResiduesInViewer(plugin, residues, mode) — builds MolScript queries and applies select/highlight Loci
focusResiduesInViewer(plugin, residues) — focuses residues to trigger ball-and-stick focus representation
clearSelection(plugin) — deselects all in 3D viewer
clearHighlight(plugin) — clears hover highlights in 3D viewer
extractChains(plugin) — iterates structure units to extract chain IDs, entity IDs, and residue sequences
extractElements(plugin) — extracts per-chain element info with entity type, comp IDs, atom/residue counts
extractMeta(plugin) — extracts structure name from model entry ID
selectChainInViewer(plugin, chainId) — selects and focuses an entire chain in the 3D viewer
showSticksForLoci(plugin, loci, tag, label) — shared builder; adds StructureSelectionFromBundle + StructureRepresentation3D ball-and-stick tagged with the given tag (replaces prior nodes with same tag)
deleteCellsByTag(plugin, tag) — deletes state-tree nodes by tag
focusInterfaceForChain(plugin, chainId, category, radius=5) — builds the contact MolScript (chain X residues within 5 Å of any non-self atom ∪ partner-side residues within 5 Å of chain X), entity-type-aware self detection; renders as 'tarantino-interface' sticks and focusSphere
clearInterfaceFocus(plugin) — deletes 'tarantino-interface' sticks
showSelectionSticks(plugin, residues) — renders sequence-selection ball-and-stick tagged 'tarantino-selection'
clearSelectionSticks(plugin) — deletes 'tarantino-selection' sticks
